org.jetel.graph.modelview

Interface MVMetadata

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MVGraphElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MVEngineMetadata

    public interface MVMetadata
extends MVGraphElement
    This is general model view to a record metadata. This model view is used by MetadataPropagationResolver.
